{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_11_01_short",
  "title": "兵藤雫 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、私のソロ曲を制作することになった……！？\nそんな、いきなり言われても……本当に私でいいの？",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどころか、遅かったくらいさ\n雫の歌唱力の高さは前から評判になっていたからな",
      "startTime": 13.8665958762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "それは言い過ぎ……\nだけど、そう言ってもらえるのは素直に嬉しい……",
      "startTime": 20.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "話はこれだけじゃないぞ。ソロ曲のリリースに合わせて\n雫のソロライブも計画しているんだ",
      "startTime": 29.4333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ソロ曲に加えて、ソロライブまで……\n現実とは思えない……もしかして、これは夢……？",
      "startTime": 35.6416727901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nほっぺた、つねってもいい……？",
      "startTime": 40.2666659038,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3000,
          "startTime": 42.2999992371
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いてててて！",
      "startTime": 42.2999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "夢じゃない……！！\n全部、現実……！",
      "startTime": 46.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いたた……信じてもらえて良かったよ……\nもし、曲やライブで希望があれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 52.5666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_11_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "私の希望……じゃあ……作詞と、衣装のデザイン……\nあと、ライブの演出もやってみたい……",
      "startTime": 62.1666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}